              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "effect": "The dero excises damaged flesh and crudely stitches wounds shut, healing themself or an ally in reach for 2d8+10 Hit Points. For 1 hour, the target has slashing weakness 2 and is immune to Dero Medicine.",
